{"tid":526443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民初選實體投票日 1月14日（日）09:00-21:00      (記得去投票表態)","createTime":"2018-01-11T15:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T12:38:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7826e7d4d3d690cc54a45d6fc7eb49ef5875c029","tid":526443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"泛民初選實體投票日 1月14日（日）09:00-21:00      (記得去投票表態)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得等帶同身分證、2017年住址證明（銀行信件、政府公函或公用服務單據）去投票。<br />\n<br />\n投票日期：2018年1月14日（日）<br />\n投票時間：09:00-21:00<br />\n<br />\n九龍西票站地點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 石硤尾邨展覽廳<br />\n(石硤尾南昌街215號石硤尾社區會堂側, 近港鐵石硤尾站A出口)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/WsZHi2kXUHR2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FWsZHi2kXUHR2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=74af640f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/WsZHi2kXUHR2</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 尖沙咀基督教協進大樓地窖<br />\n(尖沙咀加連威老道33號, 近港鐵尖沙咀站A出口)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/JwSw2UR1uHH2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FJwSw2UR1uHH2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0b11eea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/JwSw2UR1uHH2</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 港鐵黃埔站A出口<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/Vqdr582KepF2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FVqdr582KepF2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3a33cdd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/Vqdr582KepF2</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍西 及 新界東<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26230882_1583910508357980_2665145384115801832_n.jpg?oh=084621aa8ec459b5d403cfbc37361376&amp;oe=5AEF595E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26230882_1583910508357980_2665145384115801832_n.jpg%3Foh%3D084621aa8ec459b5d403cfbc37361376%26oe%3D5AEF595E&h=a50f6963&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ddad06906799f26fe638c002f82ba01fe36a5","tid":526443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T15:28:19.000Z","msg":"票站投票流程<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26169047_1664884986903423_2069740081768014259_n.jpg?oh=b6a3589c602517f9e1266318c103fb99&amp;oe=5AEC0E30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26169047_1664884986903423_2069740081768014259_n.jpg%3Foh%3Db6a3589c602517f9e1266318c103fb99%26oe%3D5AEC0E30&h=c969080f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7661260d8c576f0aa2dc0c92caf728f2921e5dfb","tid":526443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPowerForDemocracy%2F&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8fda1dfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/</a><br />\n<br />\n民主動力 Power for Democracy<br />\n昨天 19:07 發佈 &middot; <br />\n[[ 今個星期日 #民主動力 主辦 #民主派初選，約定你去投票！ ]]<br />\n<br />\n#1月14日 #上午9時至晚上9時，帶備 #身份證 及 #有效的住址證明 (2017年內的電費單、銀行單等)，到以下所屬選區的票站投票， 選出代表民主派的最強人選，重奪 #立法會補選 議席！<br />\n<br />\n[#九龍西 地方選區]<br />\n1. #基督教協進大樓地窖 (尖沙咀加連威老道33號 ) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/VvtbyBGF8ty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FVvtbyBGF8ty&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7e882343\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/VvtbyBGF8ty</a><br />\n2. #石硤尾邨展覽廳 (石硤尾南昌街215號石硤尾社區會堂側) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/35zWGst7dqr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F35zWGst7dqr&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=37013b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/35zWGst7dqr</a><br />\n3. #黃埔港鐵站A出口對出空地 (近民兆街) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/BSVx8moBUPD2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FBSVx8moBUPD2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9e000efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/BSVx8moBUPD2</a><br />\n<br />\n[#新界東 地方選區]<br />\n1. #粉嶺港鐵站A2出口地面空地 (粉嶺車站路) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/f9Qrhs73N8L2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Ff9Qrhs73N8L2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7330c8bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/f9Qrhs73N8L2</a><br />\n2. #大埔墟街市及熟食中心旁邊空地 (大埔運頭街) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/WAzR5oy43F72\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FWAzR5oy43F72&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6de421fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/WAzR5oy43F72</a><br />\n3. #將軍澳港鐵站A2出口旁邊空地 (近寶邑路) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/q5Kk1xDbpDJ2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fq5Kk1xDbpDJ2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b08e0bd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/q5Kk1xDbpDJ2</a><br />\n4. #大圍港鐵站D出口對出空地 (近富嘉花園) <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/1MAR1DJFZXm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F1MAR1DJFZXm&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=986a7f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/1MAR1DJFZXm</a><br />\n5. #香港中文大學鄭裕彤樓地下 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/qbQMjDhKiuP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FqbQMjDhKiuP2&d=P8av%2FCG3xJrvXtlxyhsLb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=303da234\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/qbQMjDhKiuP2</a><br />\n<br />\n#114民主派初選 #311立法會補選 #反DQ #抗威權<br />\n#團結一致 #抗衡建制 #重奪議席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26231809_1667908899934365_4939883015365825343_n.jpg?oh=a28d691c60c0e222d13210a4c9b4c709&amp;oe=5AE9B2D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26231809_1667908899934365_4939883015365825343_n.jpg%3Foh%3Da28d691c60c0e222d13210a4c9b4c709%26oe%3D5AE9B2D2&h=73e60264&s={SIZE}\" 